OL,3,CReview into care campus reveals
OL,4,Csafeguarding failures after woman, 60,
OL,5,Cdies
OL,7,FA review has exposed major
OL,8,Fsafeguarding failures at a Somerset
OL,9,Fcare campus run by the National
OL,10,FAutistic Society, following the death
OL,11,Fof a vulnerable woman just one year
OL,12,Fafter a separate scandal at the same
OL,13,Fsite.
OL,15,FThe 60 year-old woman, referred to in
OL,16,Fthe report via the pseudonym 'Hazel',
OL,17,Fhad been diagnosed with autism, a
OL,18,Flearning disability, and Bell's palsy.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
