OL,3,CReview into care campus reveals
OL,4,Csafeguarding failures after woman, 60,
OL,5,Cdies
OL,7,FShe died in July 2019 after choking on
OL,8,Fa sandwich at Somerset Court in Brent
OL,9,FKnoll and had lived on the campus,
OL,10,Fwhich housed multiple residential
OL,11,Funits for people with autism, since
OL,12,Fthe age of 15.
OL,14,FAn independent Safeguarding Adults
OL,15,FReview, published by the Somerset
OL,16,FSafeguarding Adults Board, concluded
OL,17,Fthat Hazel's death was preventable.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
