OL,3,CReview into care campus reveals
OL,4,Csafeguarding failures after woman, 60,
OL,5,Cdies
OL,7,FIt criticised serious shortcomings in
OL,8,Fher care, including poor risk
OL,9,Fmanagement, a lack of coordinated
OL,10,Fsupport, family engagement and failure
OL,11,Fto follow her health care plans.
OL,13,FCrucially, the report highlights that
OL,14,Fthese failings occurred just a year
OL,15,Fafter a damning safeguarding review
OL,16,Finto abuse at Mendip House, which was
OL,17,Fanother residential unit on the same
OL,18,FNational Autistic Society site.
OL,20,FStaff at Mendip House were found to
OL,21,Fhave mocked and humiliated residents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
