OL,3,CReview into care campus reveals
OL,4,Csafeguarding failures after woman, 60,
OL,5,Cdies
OL,7,FDespite national scrutiny following
OL,8,Fthe Mendip House scandal in 2018, the
OL,9,Freview found that the lessons were not
OL,10,Flearned or applied across the rest of
OL,11,Fthe campus.
OL,13,FHazel's home was affected by high
OL,14,Fstaff turnover, agency workers
OL,15,Funfamiliar with her needs, and
OL,16,Finadequate oversight particularly
OL,17,Ftroubling for someone who relied on
OL,18,Froutine and consistency to manage her
OL,19,Fanxiety.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
