OL,3,CReview into care campus reveals
OL,4,Csafeguarding failures after woman, 60,
OL,5,Cdies
OL,7,FThe report also criticised agencies
OL,8,Ffor failing to work together, failing
OL,9,Fto escalate repeated safeguarding
OL,10,Fconcerns, and for not involving
OL,11,FHazel's family or providing advocacy
OL,12,Fwhen decisions about her care were
OL,13,Fbeing made.
OL,15,FSpeech and language therapy
OL,16,Frecommendations about Hazel's choking
OL,17,Frisk were known but not properly
OL,18,Fcommunicated to all staff.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
