OL,3,CReview into care campus reveals
OL,4,Csafeguarding failures after woman, 60,
OL,5,Cdies
OL,7,FSince Hazel's death, a new Multi-
OL,8,FAgency Risk Management (MARM)
OL,9,Fframework has been introduced locally,
OL,10,Fand all campus-style services like the
OL,11,Fone Hazel lived in are being phased
OL,12,Fout nationally under the Transforming
OL,13,FCare programme.
OL,15,FThe review calls for urgent action to
OL,16,Fensure that out-of-area placements for
OL,17,Fpeople with disabilities are subject
OL,18,Fto better oversight and regular review.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
