OL,3,CReview into care campus reveals
OL,4,Csafeguarding failures after woman, 60,
OL,5,Cdies
OL,7,FIt also recommends mandatory dysphagia
OL,8,Fand autism training for all care
OL,9,Fstaff, especially those employed
OL,10,Fthrough agencies.
OL,12,FProfessor Michael Preston-Shoot,
OL,13,FIndependent Chair of the SSAB said:
OL,14,F"The Somerset Safeguarding Adults
OL,15,FBoard exists to protect people at risk
OL,16,Fof abuse and neglect and to make sure
OL,17,Flessons are learned so that necessary
OL,18,Fimprovements can be made.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
