OL,5,Cdies
OL,7,F"I want to take this opportunity to
OL,8,Foffer Hazel's family my sincere
OL,9,Fcondolences for their loss."
OL,11,FHe added: "Hazel's tragic story has
OL,12,Fhighlighted that further work is
OL,13,Frequired to sharing information across
OL,14,Four organisations to safeguard those
OL,15,Fwith support & care needs and learning
OL,16,Fdisabilities in Somerset.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
