OL,7,F"Hazel lived with us for over 40 years
OL,8,Fin one of our residential homes, and
OL,9,Fher loss was felt very deeply by the
OL,10,Fstaff who cared for her.
OL,12,F"We accept the findings and
OL,13,Frecommendations of the Safeguarding
OL,14,FAdults Review. Following Hazel's death
OL,15,Fin 2019, we reviewed and updated
OL,16,Fpolicies and systems locally and
OL,17,Fnationally.
